issues.title: False alarms triggered by overlapping thermal zones
issues.description: Safety analysis module generates false alarms when multiple thermal regions overlap. Review and optimize merge strategies.

issues.title: Edge case failures in anomaly detection
issues.description: Anomaly detection fails for edge cases involving overlapping reflective surfaces. Augment training and validate model behavior.

commits.message: Reviewed merge strategies to reduce false alarms in overlapping thermal zones.
Augmented training data for anomaly detection with overlapping reflective surfaces.

issues.title: Overfitting in deepfake detection training pipeline
issues.description: Training pipeline for deepfake detection shows overfitting to certain video styles. Expand dataset and apply regularization techniques.

issues.title: Misclassification during adversarial input testing
issues.description: Adversarial inputs with minor pixel alterations cause the deepfake detection model to misclassify. Reinforce training against adversarial examples.

commits.message: Expanded dataset and applied regularization to combat overfitting.
Added adversarial examples to training set for improved robustness.

issues.title: Pedestrian detection failures at curved crosswalks
issues.description: Model struggles to identify pedestrians at crosswalks with significant curves. Investigate curvature augmentation in training datasets.

issues.title: Inaccurate bounding boxes for high-speed objects
issues.description: Bounding box predictions lose accuracy for fast-moving pedestrians in urban environments. Investigate model latency and tuning.

commits.message: Added curved crosswalk scenarios to training datasets.
Tuned model latency for improved bounding box accuracy in high-speed scenarios.
